Ultimate Fishing Simulator
, accessing and using the websites, platforms and related services (hereinafter the “Game”).
IF YOU DO NOT AGREE WITH HOW WE USE YOUR PERSONAL DATA AS DESCRIBED IN THIS PRIVACY POLICY PLEASE DO NOT ACCESS OR PLAY THE GAME.
Please note that this Privacy Policy applies only to personal data submitted and collected online through or in relation to the Game and game platforms, and does not apply to personal data that may be collected by Ultimate Games S.A. or its affiliates offline.
